activity.requirements: Dress code: we recommend wearing comfortable shoes.
activity.attention:
• Not recommended for travelers with heart problems or other serious medical conditions
  • Please provide the full names of all travelers when booking. Failure to present a voucher with all travelers' full names at the ticket office prior to entry may result in denied entry to the Colosseum and Roman Forum.
  • We advise you to arrive on time. This allows us to guarantee a quality tour. By arriving on time, you will make the most of your time on the tour, respecting all the participants and with no risk of missing the tour.
  • No large umbrellas, large backpacks or sharp objects are allowed.
  • The group tour itinerary is not suitable for people with mobility difficulties or small children in strollers.
  • By booking this tour, you will avoid the long queues to enter the Colosseum.
  • Each traveller must present a valid passport or identity card matching the name provided at the time of booking in order to successfully enter the Colosseum and Roman Forum.
